A New Zealand couple caught their housemate rubbing his 4-5 with the woman's toothbrush on camera after suspecting someone has been sneaking in to their room, MIRROR REPORTED. The woman noticed that things were being moved around in the room and they would usually not find it the way they left it and decided to install a hidden camera.&nbsp;The couple could not believe what they found after setting up the camera. The video showed the couple's house mate sneaking in and walks into the bathroom and picks up a toothbrush. He then appears to rub the brush up against his 4-5.When the couple confronted the man he told them he has a toothbrush obsession.&nbsp;